user.biography: If there’s water you can bet I’ll try dangling my worm in it! 💦🐛 Your Friendly Neighborhood Fisherman 🎣😎 #Bass #Fishing #Adventure #Outdoors

node.text: What would you throw here? 🎣🤔 Get ready for an ABSOLUTE BANGER dropping tomo! I explore an area I’ve never fished before, it was definitely a struggle but I was fully rewarded in the end 😎 #fishing #river #fishingislife #outdoors #fishinglife
